articles.title: 'It was tough': World War II veterans return to Utah Beach to mark D-Day's 79th anniversary - ABC News
articles.description: Dozens of World War II veterans have traveled to Normandy to mark the 79th anniversary of D-Day, the decisive but deadly assault that led to the liberation of France and Western Europe from Nazi control
